--- MySQL Installation & Usage Guide ---
--- Version 1.0.0, Author Liu Yue ---

== 安装 ==

运行：sh install.sh

== 初始化 ==
a. 创建授权表
MYSQLPATH/bin/mysql_install_db --user=mysql --datadir=xxx 
// 必须要指定datadir

b. 启动mysql服务
sbin/__sensitive__mysql.sh start

c. 设置root密码
./mysqladmin -uroot password 'shrimp' --socket=/home/users/liuyue01/var/mysql/mysql.6600.sock

d. 关闭服务
bin/mysqladmin -uroot -S /home/$USER/local/mysql/dr-sep/var/mysql.sock shutdown


